Fortis Healthcare Global Buys 28.6 Percent of Lanka Hospital

-- B y   A n u s h a   O n d a a t j i e
-- 
2011-03-04T09:39:25Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-04/fortis-healthcare-global-buys-28-6-percent-of-lanka-hospital.html
Fortis Global Healthcare Holdings
Pte Ltd. bought a 28.6 percent stake in Lanka Hospital Corp.
Plc, according to a filing to the  Colombo Stock Exchange .  Fortis today bought 64.1 million shares in Lanka Hospital
at 62 rupees apiece, Bartleet Mallory Stockbrokers Pvt. Ltd.
said in the filing.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Anusha Ondaatjie in Colombo at 
 anushao@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
